I"¼<p>SARII (Simple ARtificial Intelligence Inspiration) is an artificial neural network that likes to write inspiration quotes.</p>

<p><img src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1247797253097414656/6K8-9JfP_400x400.jpg" alt="drawing" width="128" /></p>

