<h2 id="data">Data</h2>

<p>SARII has been trainned on quotes from a wide range of real authors available on <a href="https://goodreads.com">GoodReads</a></p>

<h2 id="architecure">Architecure</h2>

<p>SARII is based in a easy to train AWD-LSTM neural network architecure [<a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/1708.02182.pdf">Paper</a>] which is Long short-term memory (LSTM) Recurrent Neural Netwrok (RNN).</p>

<p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*Mr9zEA72R-LdAHtnXyZ0Eg.png" alt="AWD-LSTM" /></p>

<h2 id="twitter-bot">Twitter Bot</h2>

<p>The main goal of SARII was to compete with another accounts that like to share quotes embedded on images. So the process is not only generating a quote but automating the process of searching a image from <a href="https://unsplash.com">Unsplash</a> editing the image, putting the quote on it and sharing it on social media.</p>

<p>The final result looks like this</p>

